00:43:34,580 --> 00:43:37,940
♪A girl from the Yang family
came of age♪

861
00:43:37,940 --> 00:43:41,620
♪Raised in her chamber,
unknown to the world♪

862
00:43:41,620 --> 00:43:45,300
♪Born with stunning grace
she couldn't hide♪

863
00:43:45,300 --> 00:43:49,180
♪One day, she was chosen
to serve by his side♪

864
00:43:56,300 --> 00:44:00,900
♪She glanced back
with a smile of myriad charms♪

865
00:44:01,780 --> 00:44:06,380
♪All the palace beauties
lost their glow♪

866
00:44:12,940 --> 00:44:16,460
♪In the chilly spring,
she bathed at Huaqing Pond♪

867
00:44:16,460 --> 00:44:20,300
♪The warm spring water
slid over her silky skin♪

868
00:44:23,860 --> 00:44:27,340
♪Handmaids helped her rise
from the water♪

869
00:44:27,340 --> 00:44:31,580
♪Thus began the time
she gained the emperor's favor♪

870
00:44:34,980 --> 00:44:38,420
♪Flowing hair, a flower-bright face,
and a hairpin of glamor♪

871
00:44:38,420 --> 00:44:42,420
♪In the warm lotus canopy,
they spent spring nights together♪

872
00:44:44,020 --> 00:44:47,340
♪Those sweet nights were too short,
he rose until noon♪

873
00:44:47,340 --> 00:44:51,860
♪From then on,
he skipped the morning court♪

874
00:45:00,540 --> 00:45:03,980
♪Always at his side,
forever delighting and dining♪

875
00:45:03,980 --> 00:45:07,700
♪They spent spring on spring outings,
night on night together♪

876
00:45:07,700 --> 00:45:12,580
♪In the palace lived
three thousand beauties♪

877
00:45:15,260 --> 00:45:19,220
♪Yet all three thousand favors
were hers alone♪
